<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cyprus AML Compliance Overview & Readiness Report</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; margin: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
    h1, h2, h3 { color: #003366; text-align: center; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
    th, td { border: 1px solid #cccccc; padding: 12px; text-align: left; }
    th { background-color: #003366; color: white; }
    td { background-color: white; }
    h1 { font-size: 32px; }
    h2 { font-size: 28px; }
    h3 { font-size: 24px; color: #006699; }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .dropdown { padding: 10px; font-size: 16px; }
    .legend { font-size: 0.9em; color: #555; }
    .btn { padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #003366; color: white; border: none; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 4px; }
    .btn:hover { background-color: #0057b8; }
    .input-field { padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 100%; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px; }
    ul { list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0; }
    li { margin: 10px 0; }
    .table-container { margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .section-header { margin-top: 30px; color: #003366; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Cyprus AML Compliance Overview (5AMLD and 6AMLD)</h1>
    <h2>Implications of 5AMLD and 6AMLD for Cyprus</h2>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Directive</th>
        <th>Status in Cyprus</th>
        <th>Main Implications</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>5AMLD</td>
        <td>‚úÖ Fully implemented (Law 13(I)/2021)</td>
        <td>UBO Register, crypto sector regulation, enhanced due diligence, wider access to ownership data</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>6AMLD</td>
        <td>‚ùå Not yet transposed</td>
        <td>Criminalization of ML, company liability, wider predicate offences, tougher sanctions</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Practical Compliance Measures</h2>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Area</th>
        <th>Required Actions Now (5AMLD)</th>
        <th>Prepare for Future (6AMLD)</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>KYC/Customer Due Diligence</td>
        <td>Enhanced verification, ongoing checks</td>
        <td>Extend monitoring to new predicate offences</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>AML Policies & Procedures</td>
        <td>Updated policies, onboarding adjustments</td>
        <td>New internal rules covering corporate criminal liability</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Crypto Businesses</td>
        <td>Register with CySEC, apply AML rules</td>
        <td>Prepare additional reports for upcoming direct EU oversight</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Training</td>
        <td>Staff training on new risk indicators</td>
        <td>Criminal risk exposure training for management and staff</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Internal Controls</td>
        <td>Implement UBO monitoring, STR reporting</td>
        <td>Systems to detect/report all predicate offences</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Corporate Governance</td>
        <td>Appoint AML compliance officers, internal audits</td>
        <td>Prove active monitoring and prevention of internal money laundering</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>AML Compliance Checklist (5AMLD/6AMLD)</h2>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>‚úîÔ∏è</th>
        <th>Area</th>
        <th>Checkpoint</th>
        <th>5AMLD Compliance</th>
        <th>6AMLD Preparation</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td>UBO Register</td>
        <td>Submitted and updated beneficial ownership data?</td>
        <td>‚úÖ</td>
        <td>-</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td>KYC Processes</td>
        <td>Updated for high-risk country clients?</td>
        <td>‚úÖ</td>
        <td>üîÑ (Add new predicate crimes risk)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td>Virtual Assets</td>
        <td>Registered with CySEC if operating in crypto?</td>
        <td>‚úÖ</td>
        <td>-</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td>STR Reporting</td>
        <td>Internal procedures active?</td>
        <td>‚úÖ</td>
        <td>üîÑ (Extend to all 22 predicate offences)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td>Internal Training</td>
        <td>AML/CTF training completed in last 12 months?</td>
        <td>‚úÖ</td>
        <td>üîÑ (Add corporate liability training)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td>Risk Assessment</td>
        <td>Updated institutional risk review?</td>
        <td>‚úÖ</td>
        <td>üîÑ (Environmental crime, cybercrime risk)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td>Criminal Liability Controls</td>
        <td>Internal rules to prevent ML facilitation?</td>
        <td>‚ùå</td>
        <td>üîÑ (Mandatory under 6AMLD)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td>Board Involvement</td>
        <td>Regular AML compliance reporting to Board?</td>
        <td>‚úÖ</td>
        <td>üîÑ (Formalize reporting)</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p class="legend">
      ‚úÖ = Mandatory now<br>
      üîÑ = Start preparing now
    </p>

    <h2>Internal "AML Readiness Report" Template</h2>
    <form>
      <p><strong>Company Name:</strong> <input class="input-field" type="text" name="company_name"></p>
      <p><strong>Reporting Period:</strong> <input class="input-field" type="text" name="reporting_period"></p>

      <h3 class="section-header">1. UBO Register</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Are all UBO records updated and submitted? <input type="checkbox"></li>
        <li>Date of last update: <input type="date"></li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="section-header">2. Customer Due Diligence</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Are customer KYC files up-to-date? <input type="checkbox"></li>
        <li>EDD applied to high-risk third countries? <input type="checkbox"></li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="section-header">3. Suspicious Transaction Reporting (STR)</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>STRs filed to MOKAS this period: <input type="text" class="input-field"></li>
        <li>Number of internal reports escalated: <input type="text" class="input-field"></li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="section-header">4. Staff Training</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Date of last AML training session: <input type="date" class="input-field"></li>
        <li>Topics covered: <input type="text" class="input-field"></li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="section-header">5. Internal Controls & Governance</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Last internal AML audit performed: <input type="date" class="input-field"></li>
        <li>Findings and corrective actions taken: <input type="text" class="input-field"></li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="section-header">6. Preparation for 6AMLD</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Initial risk assessment updated for 6AMLD predicate offences? <input type="checkbox"></li>
        <li>Policies adapted for corporate criminal liability? <input type="checkbox"></li>
      </ul>

      <button type="submit" class="btn">Submit Report</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
